title: Did Kai Cenat unfollow Ray on Instagram? Social media move sparks fan speculation online
summary_full: Rumors claimed Kai Cenat unfollowed Ray and ended their friendship, but available facts show otherwise. Kai still follows Ray online, and no official statement confirms any fallout. The story spread mainly through social media speculation. Ray even recently thanked Kai during Super Bowl weekend, suggesting their bond remains strong despite the online noise.
